    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been kept in a climate-controlled environment. The paint is entirely original and flawless, while the interior still has that new-car scent with no signs of wear on the leather or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and every feature functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
